data.title: Anna May Pollock Obituary

data.text:
ANNA MAY POLLOCK (nee Tanno) age 92, beloved wife of the late Ernest R.; loving mother of Daniel (wife Andrea) and Norman (wife Linda); devoted grandmother of Damon (wife Lindsay) and Danielle and great-grandmother of Ryan and Ian; cherished daughter of the late Daniel and Filomena (nee Vaccariello) Tanno; dearest sister of the late Georgeanne Humbert and Rev. Lewis Tanno; dear aunt and great-aunt of many.

In lieu of flowers, contributions may be made in memory of Anna May to Red Tulip Project P.O. Box 322, East Claridon, OH 44033.
